<span>📅 2019</span>
</div>
<p id="detailSynopsis">The Avengers assemble once more to reverse the damage caused by Thanos and restore balance to the universe.</p>
<button class="book-now-btn" onclick="showBookingSection()">Book Now</button>
</div>
</div>

<!-- Showtimes Section -->
<div class="showtimes-section" id="bookingSection" style="display: none;">
